---
description: Do not corrupt orchestrator MCP stdio or checkpoint files.
globs:
  - "mcp-server/**/*.ts"
  - ".pi-orchestrator/**/*"
---

- Never add `console.log` to MCP server code on stdout; use `process.stderr` for diagnostics.
- Do not edit `mcp-server/dist/` by hand; edit `src/` and run `npm run build`.
- Do not write directly to `.pi-orchestrator/checkpoint.json`; use `orch_*` MCP tools.
